@DrewGooden this video, apart from being the usual amount of fun and funny, was my favourite so far because of the cat bit. I'm a cat mom but I also volunteer full time at the local shelter cattery and I've been missing my shelter cats so much. Seeing you play with her and treat her like I expect any good cat parent would was so heartwarming. And also, seeing that every cat parent inevitably has giant cat kibble bags just in the house in plain view is something I connected with on a personal level. 😅
Love your content, dude. Stay safe.
